# 5. **BACKEND TECHNOLOGIES & STRUCTURE**

## **Technologies Used:**

| Technology | Purpose |
|------------|---------|
| **Node.js** | JavaScript runtime |
| **Express.js** | Web framework |
| **MongoDB + Mongoose** | Database + ODM |
| **JWT (jsonwebtoken)** | Authentication tokens |
| **bcryptjs** | Password hashing |
| **Multer** | File uploads (CVs, photos) |
| **Puppeteer** | HTML to PDF conversion |
| **pdf-parse** | Extract text from PDF CVs |
| **Nodemailer** | Send emails (verification, password reset) |
| **node-cron** | Scheduled tasks (refresh career data) |
| **cors** | Cross-origin requests |
| **dotenv** | Environment variables |

## **Folder Structure:**

```
backend/
├── config/
│   └── database.js            # MongoDB connection
│
├── models/                     # Mongoose schemas (6 models)
│   ├── User.js                # User accounts + CV data
│   ├── UserProfile.js         # Career assessment answers
│   ├── Resume.js              # Tailored resumes
│   ├── JobAnalysis.js         # CV vs Job comparisons
│   ├── ChatSession.js         # Chat conversation threads
│   ├── ChatMessage.js         # Individual messages
│   └── ApiSettings.js         # Admin API keys
│
├── controllers/                # Business logic
│   ├── authController.js      # Register, login, forgot password
│   ├── profileController.js   # User profile, CV upload, analysis
│   ├── careerController.js    # Career recommendations, skills list
│   ├── analysisController.js  # CV vs Job analysis
│   ├── chatController.js      # Chat sessions, messages
│   ├── resumeController.js    # Resume builder, PDF generation
│   └── adminController.js     # Admin functions (users, resumes, chats)
