# 6. **DATABASE DESIGN (6 MODELS)**

## **Model 1: User**

```javascript
{
  name: String,                    // Full name (first + last)
  email: String,                  // Unique, lowercase
  password: String,               // Hashed with bcrypt
  emailVerified: Boolean,         // Email verification status
  emailVerificationToken: String,
  resetPasswordToken: String,
  
  // Profile fields
  photoUrl: String,
  phone: String,
  location: String,
  
  // CV fields (AI-extracted)
  cvUrl: String,                  // Path to uploaded PDF
  cvAnalyzed: Boolean,
  cvSkills: [String],             // Skills extracted by AI
  cvExtractedText: String,
  cvExperience: [Object],         // Work history extracted
  cvSummary: String,
  cvYearsOfExperience: Number,
  cvExperienceLevel: String,      // junior/mid/senior/lead
  cvStrengths: [String],
  
  // Saved CVs from Resume Builder
  savedCVs: [{
    filename: String,
    originalName: String,
    path: String,
    uploadedAt: Date,
    formData: Object,             // Full resume form data
    template: String,             // modern/classic/executive
    isTailoredResume: Boolean,
    forJobTitle: String
  }],
  
  // Career assessment profile reference
  profileId: String,
  profile: {
    skills: String,
    interests: String,
    goalJob: String,
    experienceLevel: String
  },
  
  createdAt: Date,
  lastLogin: Date
}
```

## **Model 2: UserProfile (Career Assessment)**

```javascript
{
  skills: String,                 // Comma-separated
  interests: String,              // Comma-separated
  goalJob: String,
  experienceLevel: String,        // beginner/intermediate/advanced
  profileId: String,              // Unique (e.g., PROF-1234567890-1234)
  createdAt: Date,
  updatedAt: Date
}
```

## **Model 3: Resume (Tailored Resumes)**

```javascript
{
  userId: ObjectId,               // Reference to User
  title: String,
  originalCV: String,             // Path to original CV
  tailoredResume: String,         // Path to generated PDF
  jobTitle: String,
  companyName: String,
  jobDescription: String,
  tailoredContent: Object,        // AI-generated content
  template: String,
  createdAt: Date
}
```

## **Model 4: JobAnalysis (CV vs Job)**

```javascript
{
  userId: ObjectId,
  jobTitle: String,
  companyName: String,
  requiredSkills: [String],
  experienceRequired: String,
  jobDescription: String,
  cvSource: String,               // Where CV came from
  analysisResult: {
    matchPercentage: Number,
    matchedSkills: [String],
    missingSkills: [String],
    strengths: [String],
    weaknesses: [String],
    recommendations: [String],
    summary: String,
    interviewQuestions: [String]
  },
  createdAt: Date
}
```

## **Model 5: ChatSession**

```javascript
{
  userId: ObjectId,
  title: String,                  // Auto-generated from first message
  createdAt: Date,
  updatedAt: Date
}
```

## **Model 6: ChatMessage**

```javascript
{
  sessionId: ObjectId,            // Reference to ChatSession
  userId: ObjectId,
  role: String,                   // 'user' or 'assistant'
  content: String,
  createdAt: Date
}
```

## **Model 7: ApiSettings (Admin)**

```javascript
{
  geminiApiKey: String,           // Stored encrypted
  adminKeyHash: String,           // bcrypt hash of admin key
  adminKeyLastUpdated: Date,
  lastUpdated: Date,
  updatedBy: String
}
```

